{"tid":828252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[HK No IT】Tap＆Go手機錢包餘額突變負數　HKT認系統出問題","createTime":"2018-09-19T13:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T06:36:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ae6f96a6dddf72dcab7a7e9cac5f6c74e42d24c","tid":828252,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"香港電訊(HKT)旗下的Tap&amp;Go「拍住賞」手機付款程式系統今日(19日)一度出錯，多名用戶指其手機錢包餘額「正數變負數」，有人更指餘額突然變成「負2000元」。香港電訊證實，部分Tap&amp;Go「拍住賞」客戶的手機錢包餘額及交易紀錄，今日曾短暫出現問題，但下午已恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n在「Tap&amp;Go by HKT拍住賞」的Facebook專頁，今有多名用戶留言，指其儲值金額消失不見，甚至變成負數，有人稱「無啦啦啲錢無曬(晒)」、「我無咗千幾蚊」，亦有人指餘額本應約有500港元，「但變左(咗)負1千多d(啲)」；「我都係，無哂(晒)錢，仲要負2000，咩事呀」。<br />\n<br />\n香港電訊回覆東網查詢時指，部分客戶手機錢包餘額及交易紀錄今日曾短暫出現問題，但較早時已恢復正常，強調系統的安全性一直完好，客戶的手機錢包在今次事件中都安全<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180919/bkn-20180919213019113-0919_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180919%2Fbkn-20180919213019113-0919_00822_001.html&d=CcPOoo3GE3umE%2F%2BZ%2BO3uGjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=08540b6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180919/bkn-20180919213019113-0919_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e24243d0a6feb7d919ea3d99890282524fc3ba71","tid":828252,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f008c1928aabc6252b95c4f5d35af5f040c744e","tid":828252,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76896f0bc8ed3e5bfc9338def68bcc70dbbfc9f3","tid":828252,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f008c1928aabc6252b95c4f5d35af5f040c744e","tid":828252,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/sc